# World Boss — Title Team Definitions
# 45 teams: 4 tiers per boss (11 bosses) + 1 champion
# Title IDs 1-44 = boss tiers, 45 = champion
# Each boss: IDs (boss-1)*4 + 1..4 → Slayer/Conqueror/Vanquisher/Nemesis

# ============================================================================
# HOLLOW KING (Boss 1) — Gray theme
# ============================================================================
team add wb.t_hk1
team modify wb.t_hk1 prefix {text:"Hollow King Slayer ",color:"gray"}
